snippet.title: Homestead Arcana - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description: Here's your look at Homestead Arcana, an upcoming third-person exploration farming simulation game coming to PC and Xbox Game Pass for Xbox Series X/S and PC via Steam. Check out the announcement trailer to learn more about the game, including a look at the world, the presence that threatens it, and what you can expect when you take on the role of Billie, a witch farmer, on your quest to save the land.
